    Yaddns
==============

Generating compilation tools with autotools
-------------------------------------------

 ./autogen.sh

Compilation/Installation
-------------------------------------------

 ./configure
 make
 make install

Usage
-------------------------------------------

 * Edit yaddns.conf file
 * Launch yaddns like this:
   /usr/bin/yaddns -f /etc/yaddns.conf -p /var/run/yaddns.pid
   (type /usr/bin/yaddns --help for more informations)

Compilation tricks for developpers
-------------------------------------------

 - To have debug messages and -g CFLAGS, set the DEBUG flag with this command:
    ./configure --enable-debug

 - If you want to compile and execute test programs from tests/ directory, type:
    make check

